'''輪班工作睡眠紊亂'''（Shift work sleep disorder，簡稱SWSD）是[[生理節奏睡眠紊亂|生理節奏睡眠紊亂]]的一種，患者通常為因需[[輪班工作制|輪班工作]]而經常轉換工作和睡眠時間、或長期於非日間工作的人。

這些對睡眠規律的重覆干擾，會導致患者[[失眠|失眠]]甚或患上[[嗜睡症|嗜睡症]]（Hypersomnia）。早睡早起的人通常都不易適應夜班工作，同樣，[[夜貓子|夜貓子]]亦很難習慣早起上早班。

2007年一個由[[國際癌症研究機構|國際癌症研究機構]]領導的研究顯示，輪班工作會誘發[[癌症|癌症]]<ref>[http://www.iarc.fr/en/Media-Centre/IARC-Press-Releases/Communiques-recents/IARC-Monographs-Programme-finds-cancer-hazards-associated-with-shiftwork-painting-and-firefighting 國際癌症研究機構新聞稿] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090404045442/http://www.iarc.fr/en/Media-Centre/IARC-Press-Releases/Communiques-recents/IARC-Monographs-Programme-finds-cancer-hazards-associated-with-shiftwork-painting-and-firefighting |date=2009-04-04 }}</ref>。

中樞興奮劑[[莫達非尼|莫達非尼]]獲[[美國食品藥品監督管理局|美國食品藥品監督管理局]]（FDA）認可用於治療輪班工作睡眠紊亂及[[發作性嗜睡病|發作性嗜睡病（渴睡症）]]等睡眠紊亂<ref>Erman MK, Rosenberg R, For The U S Modafinil Shift Work Sleep Disorder Study Group. "Modafinil for excessive sleepiness associated with chronic shift work sleep disorder: effects on patient functioning and health-related quality of life." ''Primary Care Companion to the Journal of Clinical Psychiatry'' 2007;9(3):188-94. [http://www.psychiatrist.com/pcc/pccpdf/v09n03/v09n0304.pdf Full Text] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715131322/http://www.psychiatrist.com/pcc/pccpdf/v09n03/v09n0304.pdf |date=2011-07-15 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Czeisler CA, Walsh JK, Roth T, Hughes RJ, Wright KP, Kingsbury L, Arora S, Schwartz JRL, Niebler GE, Dinges DF |title=Modafinil for Excessive Sleepiness Associated with Shift-Work Sleep Disorder |journal=N Engl J Med |volume=353 |issue=5 |pages=476–486 |pmid=16079371 |url=http://content.nejm.org/cgi/content/abstract/353/5/476 |doi=10.1056/NEJMoa041292 |date=August 2005 |access-date=2010-07-31 |archive-date=2010-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100624153659/http://content.nejm.org/cgi/content/abstract/353/5/476 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>"Provigil (Modafinil) Site." 24 December 1998 [http://www.provigil.com/pat/default.aspx] {{Wayback|url=http://www.provigil.com/pat/default.aspx |date=20080913011232 }}.</ref>。 

